name: ✴ 𝕾𝖙𝖆𝖗 𝕶𝖎𝖓𝖌 ✴
description:
✴ Portrait of Star King

Star King is imprisoned by his own throne. His own expectation, idealism and grandiosity. What would he be if he got up of the rightful throne?

✴[MAD GOD]✴ is an original dark fantasy series consisting of blood and beautiful creatures portraying their life, their pride, and their attitude.
